# 13 Swift Distributed ActorsSampleLetItCrash	0x000000010a64f1db	 atos:closure #1 in faultyWorkerBehavior() (in Swift Distributed ActorsSampleLetItCrash) (/Users/ktoso/code/sact/Sources/Swift Distributed ActorsSampleLetItCrash/main.swift:0)
